{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b0f102fa7c","title":"周恩来李先念对北京市中学生两派代表的讲话","origin":"1967年8月25日红代会清华井冈山一部第三动态组编《动态》第132期","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ae4020537","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"b0f102fa7c"}],"tags":[{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2a17ba0492","type":"title","text":"周恩来李先念对北京市中学生两派代表的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"},{"id":"a29aaee73f","type":"authors","text":"周恩来李先念","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"},{"id":"df1273a546","type":"appellation","text":"〖八月十九日下午，在人民大会堂揪斗谭震林大会上，周总理、李先念副总理对中学革命派代表作了重要指示。摘录如下。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"},{"id":"2c819157fc","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理说：你们43派、44派要联合起来共同对付刘邓。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"},{"id":"0723dcfe2f","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念同志说：你们为什么不联合？你们对刘邓是一致的吧？你们对彭、罗、陆、杨反党集团是一致的吧？你们都是要高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗的吧？那你们为什么还不联合呢？联合起来批刘邓嘛！联合起来有力量。你们对老红卫兵要做工作。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"},{"id":"2e3e16f97b","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念并询问了“联动”活动情况。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c"}],"page":{"id":"3f9a41df91","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b0f102fa7c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}